  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive when it intends to publish a proposal for legislation on protecting rural schools.</p>

</ques>


<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2008-04-02.S3W-10929.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80400" speakername="Maureen Watt" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-08/wa0402.htm#2">

  <p>We intend to publish a set of proposals for comment in the form of a Consultation Paper at the end of April.</p>

</reply>
